data.title: Milestones in the life of Ernest Hemingway
data.meta_description: 1899 Ernest Miller Hemingway was born on July 21st to Dr. Clarence and Grace Hall Hemingway in Oak Park, Illinois. 1917 Hemingway graduates high school and in October begins reporting for the Kansas City Star.
